Package: multiplexILP
Type: Package
Title: Multiplex PCR Design Using Integer Linear Programming
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-03-08
Authors@R: c(
    person("First", "Last", email = "limeng49631@aliyun.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Tools for designing multiplex PCR assays using Integer Linear Programming (ILP). 
  Provides functions to generate ILP models for primer selection, optimize constraints,
  and parse solver outputs. Supports both single-primer and primer-pair approaches with 
  multi-channel fluorescence considerations.
